  "prompt": "What are the signs that a Taurus man really likes you?",
  "response": "A Taurus man is known for being reliable, practical, and sometimes a bit reserved. When a Taurus man is interested in you, he will show it through his actions and behaviors. Here are some signs that a Taurus man really likes you:\n\n1. **He spends quality time with you**: Taurus men value their time and comfort, so if he consistently makes time to be with you, it's a strong sign of his interest. He will enjoy simple, relaxing activities with you, like watching a movie at home or going for a walk in nature.\n\n2. **He is physically affectionate**: Taurus men are sensual and tactile, so he will often show his affection through physical touch. He might hold your hand, give you hugs, or find excuses to be close to you.\n\n3. **He is protective and caring**: A Taurus man who likes you will be protective and take care of your needs. He might offer to help you with tasks, make sure you're comfortable, or be concerned about your well-being.\n\n4. **He shares his interests with you**: If a Taurus man likes you, he will want to share his hobbies and interests with you. He might invite you to join him in activities he enjoys or talk to you about his passions.\n\n5. **He is consistent and reliable**: Taurus men are known for their reliability, so if he likes you, he will be consistent in his actions and words. He will keep his promises and show up when he says he will.\n\n6. **He opens up emotionally**: While Taurus men can be reserved, if he likes you, he will slowly open up and share his thoughts and feelings with you. He might talk about his dreams, fears, or personal experiences.\n\n7. **He introduces you to his friends and family**: Taurus men value their close relationships, so if he introduces you to his friends and family, it's a sign that he sees a future with you.\n\n8. **He is generous with gifts and gestures**: Taurus men show their affection through tangible gestures, so he might surprise you with thoughtful gifts or plan special outings for the two of you.\n\n9. **He is jealous or possessive**: While this can be a negative trait, a Taurus man might show signs of jealousy or possessiveness if he really likes you. He might want to make sure you're only spending time with him.\n\n10. **He talks about the future with you**: If a Taurus man likes you, he will start to include you in his future plans. He might talk about trips you could take together or discuss long-term goals.\n\nRemember, everyone is different, and these signs might vary from person to person. The best way to know if a Taurus man likes you is to communicate openly and honestly with him.",
